OL,3,CScottish election: SNP predicted fifth
OL,4,Cconsecutive win
OL,6,FThe Scottish Liberal Democrats have
OL,7,Fwon the first seat announced in the
OL,8,FScottish election, with Liam McArthur
OL,9,Fholding the Orkney Islands.
OL,11,FAt the last Scottish election, the
OL,12,Fparty secured four seats overall, the
OL,13,Fsmallest amount by any major party.
OL,15,FIn the final polls conducted before
OL,16,Fpeople cast their vote on Thursday,
OL,17,Fthe Scottish National Party (SNP) was
OL,18,Fpredicted to be on track to win its
OL,19,Ffifth consecutive election, but fell
OL,20,Fshort of an overall majority -
OL,21,Fsomething they haven't won since 2011.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
