OL,3,CScottish election: SNP predicted fifth
OL,4,Cconsecutive win
OL,6,FIn the 2024 general election, the SNP
OL,7,Flost all six Glasgow seats to Labour.
OL,9,FHow Scottish Labour fares in this
OL,10,Felection will have national
OL,11,Framifications for the prime minister
OL,12,Ftoo, after its Scottish leader, Anas
OL,13,FSarwar, called for Starmer's
OL,14,Fresignation over the Mandelson
OL,15,Fscandal, distancing himself from the
OL,16,Fnational leader throughout the
OL,17,Fcampaign.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
