OL,3,CScottish election: SNP predicted fifth
OL,4,Cconsecutive win
OL,6,FThe results of Thursday's election
OL,7,Fcould spell another defeat for the pro-
OL,8,Funion parties after the SNP's John
OL,9,FSwinney said he will seek to have
OL,10,Fanother Scottish Independence
OL,11,FReferendum by 2028 if his party
OL,12,Fperforms well.
OL,14,FThis agenda is sure to be backed in
OL,15,FHolyrood by however many Green MSPs
OL,16,Fget elected, with co-leaders Ross
OL,17,FGreer and Gilian Mackay saying they
OL,18,Fwill support the SNP on this issue.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
