OL,3,CScottish election: SNP predicted fifth
OL,4,Cconsecutive win
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FScotland is divided into 73
OL,12,Fconstituencies and elects one MSP from
OL,13,Feach of these.
OL,15,FThese constituencies are divided
OL,16,Facross eight Scottish regions, and a
OL,17,Ffurther seven MSPs are elected from
OL,18,Feach of these to make a total of 129.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
