OL,3,CScottish election: SNP predicted fifth
OL,4,Cconsecutive win
OL,6,FResults on a constituency level are
OL,7,Fharder to compare in Scotland this
OL,8,Fyear, with many boundaries being
OL,9,Fredrawn to accommodate population
OL,10,Fgrowth and shifts, ensuring the
OL,11,Felectorate size of each area remains
OL,12,Froughly equal.
OL,14,FForty-two constituencies changed
OL,15,Fboundaries, three changed in name
OL,16,Fonly, and 28 remained the same.
OL,18,FOf the current eight regions, only Mid
OL,19,FScotland and Fife remained unchanged.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
