OL,3,CScottish election: SNP predicted fifth
OL,4,Cconsecutive win
OL,6,FFive regions had minor boundary
OL,7,Fchanges, and two had boundary and name
OL,8,Fchanges.=
OL,10,FScottish MSPs sit separately from
OL,11,FWestminster's National MPs and govern
OL,12,Fdevolved political matters in Scotland
OL,13,F(like justice, health and education)
OL,14,Ffrom Holyrood.
OL,16,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,17,Four political experts are across all
OL,18,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,19,Fto the latest episode below...
